                      "body": "The EDW Activity Fee Extract process (Zena Job: OPTUM_EDW_ACTIVITY_FEE_ANALYSIS_EXTRACT_MONTHLY_000, DataStage job: EdwActivityFeeExtrCntl) can not run while there is another process listed on the P_RUN_CYC as running.\n\nSource = 'EDW'\nTarget =  'OPTUM'\nSubj = 'MEMBERSHIP'\nFrequency = 'MONTHLY'",
                      "blobFilenames": " ",
                      "fromemail": {
                        "value": "@pipeline().globalParameters.gbl_param_fromemail",
                        "type": "Expression"
